    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12550.0,
      "end_time": 13420.0,
      "text": "Else here."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13420.0,
      "end_time": 15220.0,
      "text": "And in this video, we&#39;ll be exploring"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15220.0,
      "end_time": 17950.0,
      "text": "the statement of changes in equity under IFRS."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17950.0,
      "end_time": 20440.0,
      "text": "First, let&#39;s remind ourselves of the proper order"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20440.0,
      "end_time": 22030.0,
      "text": "of the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22030.0,
      "end_time": 23800.0,
      "text": "The Income Statement comes first."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23800.0,
      "end_time": 26060.0,
      "text": "The profit or loss at the bottom of the statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26060.0,
      "end_time": 28300.0,
      "text": "which is a measure of a company&#39;s performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28300.0,
      "end_time": 30250.0,
      "text": "is the opening number in the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 30250.0,
      "end_time": 31900.0,
      "text": "of Comprehensive Income."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31900.0,
      "end_time": 33850.0,
      "text": "This statement then adds or deducts"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 33850.0,
      "end_time": 35590.0,
      "text": "unrealized gains or losses to provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 35590.0,
      "end_time": 37840.0,
      "text": "a broader definition of profit or loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 37840.0,
      "end_time": 40772.0,
      "text": "one that includes both realized and unrealized amounts."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40772.0,
      "end_time": 42730.0,
      "text": "The unrealized gains or losses on the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 42730.0,
      "end_time": 45940.0,
      "text": "of Comprehensive Income are then transferred to the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 45940.0,
      "end_time": 47490.0,
      "text": "of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 47490.0,
      "end_time": 50740.0,
      "text": "Company&#39;s following IFRS must prepare a Statement of Changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 50740.0,
      "end_time": 53950.0,
      "text": "in Equity, which reports how profits, dividends, shares,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 53950.0,
      "end_time": 56800.0,
      "text": "and other items have affected shareholders&#39; equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 56800.0,
      "end_time": 58540.0,
      "text": "Information from this statement helps"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 58540.0,
      "end_time": 61660.0,
      "text": "users watch and assess equity so they can make decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 61660.0,
      "end_time": 63084.0,
      "text": "about financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 63084.0,
      "end_time": 65500.0,
      "text": "In order to understand the Statement of Changes in Equity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 65500.0,
      "end_time": 69190.0,
      "text": "we must first understand what makes up the element equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 69190.0,
      "end_time": 71580.0,
      "text": "Equity is made up of two or more items."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 71580.0,
      "end_time": 73510.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll cover the three most common"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 73510.0,
      "end_time": 76150.0,
      "text": "and save the others for future videos."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 76150.0,
      "end_time": 78670.0,
      "text": "Share capital represents the amount of cash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 78670.0,
      "end_time": 81400.0,
      "text": "goods, or services a company received in exchange"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 81400.0,
      "end_time": 83110.0,
      "text": "for a company&#39;s shares."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 83110.0,
      "end_time": 84910.0,
      "text": "The most common form of equity is"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 84910.0,
      "end_time": 88000.0,
      "text": "when shares are sold to the public in exchange for cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 88000.0,
      "end_time": 90550.0,
      "text": "This is called a direct investment by the shareholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 90550.0,
      "end_time": 93070.0,
      "text": "because the shareholders choose to invest directly"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 93070.0,
      "end_time": 96460.0,
      "text": "in the company by buying the shares of the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 96460.0,
      "end_time": 98890.0,
      "text": "Shareholders indirectly contribute capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 98890.0,
      "end_time": 101077.0,
      "text": "when the company decides to retain profit"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 101077.0,
      "end_time": 102910.0,
      "text": "instead of paying it out to the shareholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 102910.0,
      "end_time": 104650.0,
      "text": "in the form of dividends."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 104650.0,
      "end_time": 108020.0,
      "text": "This indirect investment is called retained earnings."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 108020.0,
      "end_time": 110050.0,
      "text": "Retained earnings is increased by profit"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 110050.0,
      "end_time": 111610.0,
      "text": "and decreased by dividends paid out"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 111610.0,
      "end_time": 113860.0,
      "text": "to shareholders as well as losses from the Income"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 113860.0,
      "end_time": 114820.0,
      "text": "Statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 114820.0,
      "end_time": 116770.0,
      "text": "The amount of retained earnings represents"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 116770.0,
      "end_time": 118990.0,
      "text": "all past profits kept in the business"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 118990.0,
      "end_time": 122950.0,
      "text": "to help a company grow less all past dividends paid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 122950.0,
      "end_time": 125750.0,
      "text": "as well as losses."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 125750.0,
      "end_time": 127840.0,
      "text": "Another item in equity is accumulated"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 127840.0,
      "end_time": 129639.0,
      "text": "other comprehensive income."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 129639.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132330.0,
      "text": "This is the total of all unrealized gains and losses"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 132330.0,
      "end_time": 134080.0,
      "text": "from the Statement of Comprehensive Income"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 134080.0,
      "end_time": 136120.0,
      "text": "since the company began."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 136120.0,
      "end_time": 138490.0,
      "text": "This amount is increased by unrealized gains"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138490.0,
      "end_time": 140920.0,
      "text": "and decreased by unrealized losses."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 140920.0,
      "end_time": 143620.0,
      "text": "Now that we understand the items that make up the equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 143620.0,
      "end_time": 146200.0,
      "text": "element, let&#39;s take a look at the structure of the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 146200.0,
      "end_time": 147700.0,
      "text": "of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 147700.0,
      "end_time": 150410.0,
      "text": "As always, the statement starts with the heading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 150410.0,
      "end_time": 152180.0,
      "text": "which must include the company name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 152180.0,
      "end_time": 153850.0,
      "text": "the title of the financial statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 153850.0,
      "end_time": 155620.0,
      "text": "and the time period covered."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 155620.0,
      "end_time": 157690.0,
      "text": "Notice that this statement is set up in columns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 157690.0,
      "end_time": 160720.0,
      "text": "starting with shares and ending with a total column."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 160720.0,
      "end_time": 162640.0,
      "text": "The order of the columns must be the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 162640.0,
      "end_time": 164560.0,
      "text": "as the order of these items as they"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 164560.0,
      "end_time": 166780.0,
      "text": "are listed on the Statement of Financial Position"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 166780.0,
      "end_time": 169330.0,
      "text": "under the shareholders&#39; equity section."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 169330.0,
      "end_time": 171100.0,
      "text": "The body of the statement always starts"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 171100.0,
      "end_time": 173060.0,
      "text": "with the beginning balances."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 173060.0,
      "end_time": 175510.0,
      "text": "These beginning balances are the closing balances"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 175510.0,
      "end_time": 177550.0,
      "text": "from the prior year statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 177550.0,
      "end_time": 179860.0,
      "text": "Next, items that impact the different columns"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 179860.0,
      "end_time": 181540.0,
      "text": "are added or deducted."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 181540.0,
      "end_time": 184210.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at each column individually so we can better"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 184210.0,
      "end_time": 187390.0,
      "text": "understand which items must be taken into account."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 187390.0,
      "end_time": 190150.0,
      "text": "First, let&#39;s focus on the Share Capital column."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 190150.0,
      "end_time": 192940.0,
      "text": "Here we denote it as common shares."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 192940.0,
      "end_time": 195010.0,
      "text": "The beginning balance comes from the prior year"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 195010.0,
      "end_time": 196810.0,
      "text": "statement of changes in equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 196810.0,
      "end_time": 199900.0,
      "text": "Notice that the only things that impact share capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 199900.0,
      "end_time": 203020.0,
      "text": "are the transactions that cause share capital to change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 203020.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "here the issue of shares and the repurchase of shares."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 207910.0,
      "text": "This makes sense because we are trying"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 207910.0,
      "end_time": 211600.0,
      "text": "to show users details of what caused share capital to change"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 211600.0,
      "end_time": 213444.0,
      "text": "over a period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 213444.0,
      "end_time": 215110.0,
      "text": "The closing balance for the current year"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 215110.0,
      "end_time": 216610.0,
      "text": "will be transferred to the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 216610.0,
      "end_time": 218420.0,
      "text": "of Financial Position."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 218420.0,
      "end_time": 221030.0,
      "text": "Next, we&#39;ll look at the Retained Earnings column."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 221030.0,
      "end_time": 223940.0,
      "text": "Again, opening balances come from the prior year Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 223940.0,
      "end_time": 225896.0,
      "text": "of Changes in Equity and closing balance"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 225896.0,
      "end_time": 227270.0,
      "text": "are transferred to this Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 227270.0,
      "end_time": 229070.0,
      "text": "of Financial Position."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 229070.0,
      "end_time": 231690.0,
      "text": "Where does the profit for the year come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 231690.0,
      "end_time": 233690.0,
      "text": "Well, the profit or loss on the Income Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 233690.0,
      "end_time": 237020.0,
      "text": "is added or deducted from the opening retained earnings."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 237020.0,
      "end_time": 239810.0,
      "text": "Here we took the profit of $17,100"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 239810.0,
      "end_time": 241670.0,
      "text": "from the Income Statement and added it"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 241670.0,
      "end_time": 244670.0,
      "text": "to the opening retained earnings from the prior year."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 244670.0,
      "end_time": 247220.0,
      "text": "We also deducted the dividends declared or paid"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 247220.0,
      "end_time": 249950.0,
      "text": "to shareholders because they represent a payout of profit"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 249950.0,
      "end_time": 251480.0,
      "text": "to the shareholders."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 251480.0,
      "end_time": 254330.0,
      "text": "Next, we look at the Accumulated Other Comprehensive Income"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 254330.0,
      "end_time": 255320.0,
      "text": "column."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 255320.0,
      "end_time": 258200.0,
      "text": "The opening balance again come from the prior year&#39;s closing"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 258200.0,
      "end_time": 260600.0,
      "text": "balance on the Statement of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 260600.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262514.0,
      "text": "Then, the unrealized gains and losses"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 262514.0,
      "end_time": 264680.0,
      "text": "that were detailed on the Statement of Comprehensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 264680.0,
      "end_time": 267470.0,
      "text": "Income are added or deducted from the opening balance"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 267470.0,
      "end_time": 269810.0,
      "text": "to obtain the closing balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 269810.0,
      "end_time": 272510.0,
      "text": "It is very important to notice that the actual amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 272510.0,
      "end_time": 275480.0,
      "text": "of other comprehensive income, the amount at the bottom"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 275480.0,
      "end_time": 277460.0,
      "text": "of the Statement of Comprehensive Income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 277460.0,
      "end_time": 280220.0,
      "text": "never shows up on the Statement of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 280220.0,
      "end_time": 281990.0,
      "text": "To see this clearly, let&#39;s quickly"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 281990.0,
      "end_time": 284340.0,
      "text": "flip back to the Statement of Comprehensive Income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 284340.0,
      "end_time": 286890.0,
      "text": "which we covered in a previous video."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 286890.0,
      "end_time": 288710.0,
      "text": "Notice that the total comprehensive income"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 288710.0,
      "end_time": 291230.0,
      "text": "amount is $18,200."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 291230.0,
      "end_time": 293180.0,
      "text": "This number never shows up in the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 293180.0,
      "end_time": 294410.0,
      "text": "of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 294410.0,
      "end_time": 297140.0,
      "text": "In fact, it never shows up anywhere else."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 297140.0,
      "end_time": 300591.0,
      "text": "Instead, only the individual amounts of the unrealized gains"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 300591.0,
      "end_time": 302840.0,
      "text": "and losses are transferred to the Statement of Changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 302840.0,
      "end_time": 305810.0,
      "text": "in Equity under the Accumulated Other Comprehensive Income"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 305810.0,
      "end_time": 306860.0,
      "text": "column."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 306860.0,
      "end_time": 308690.0,
      "text": "These individual amounts are the ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 308690.0,
      "end_time": 310940.0,
      "text": "transferred to the Statement of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 310940.0,
      "end_time": 314270.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s important to remember this when you develop the statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 314270.0,
      "end_time": 316370.0,
      "text": "Going back to the Statement of Changes in Equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 316370.0,
      "end_time": 319980.0,
      "text": "in its entirety, we can see that at the bottom of the statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 319980.0,
      "end_time": 321980.0,
      "text": "we have all the amounts that will be transferred"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 321980.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "to the shareholders&#39; equity section of the Statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 327370.0,
      "text": "of Financial Position"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 327370.0,
      "end_time": 329650.0,
      "text": "Pause the video to answer the Check Your Understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 329650.0,
      "end_time": 332240.0,
      "text": "question."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 332240.0,
      "end_time": 335160.0,
      "text": "What would be the company&#39;s ending retained earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 335160.0,
      "end_time": 336500.0,
      "text": "given the amounts provided?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 341700.0,
      "end_time": 344490.0,
      "text": "A is incorrect because it includes the gain"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 344490.0,
      "end_time": 346390.0,
      "text": "from revaluing investments."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 346390.0,
      "end_time": 349320.0,
      "text": "And this item belongs only in the Accumulated Other"
