      "text": "paid and less the expenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 370440.0,
      "end_time": 373320.0,
      "text": "There are many uses for the Statement of Changes in Equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 373320.0,
      "end_time": 376050.0,
      "text": "But right now we&#39;ll focus only on the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 376050.0,
      "end_time": 379560.0,
      "text": "from the Retained Earnings column and how it is used."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 379560.0,
      "end_time": 381900.0,
      "text": "Investors use information about retained earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 381900.0,
      "end_time": 384330.0,
      "text": "to predict future dividend payouts."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 384330.0,
      "end_time": 386130.0,
      "text": "They also use it to see if the company is"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 386130.0,
      "end_time": 389280.0,
      "text": "retaining enough profit for future expansion."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 389280.0,
      "end_time": 391530.0,
      "text": "Lenders use it to determine if dividend payouts are"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 391530.0,
      "end_time": 395090.0,
      "text": "appropriate and leave enough cash for debt repayment."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 395090.0,
      "end_time": 397860.0,
      "text": "Other creditors use retained earnings information"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 397860.0,
      "end_time": 400050.0,
      "text": "to see if the company is investing profit back"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 400050.0,
      "end_time": 403410.0,
      "text": "into the company for future expansion or growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 403410.0,
      "end_time": 405840.0,
      "text": "As you already know, the Statement of Changes in Equity"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 405840.0,
